      ('3313d665-ca4d-42b1-843f-1d7a94eaf7c6', '970abe82-b8b5-4ba0-bd8e-2a283ca827b2', 'description', 'This framework defines a structured set of governance, risk management, and security controls aligned with SOC 2 Trust Services Criteria focused on the Security principle. It establishes requirements and controls for governance oversight, risk assessment, communication, monitoring, access management, system operations, change management, and third‑party risk management. The framework is intended to help organizations design, implement, and maintain effective internal controls that protect information systems and sensitive data from unauthorized access, misuse, disruption, or disclosure while supporting audit readiness for SOC 2 assessments.', '2026-04-06T15:44:43.340321', '2026-04-09T09:56:22.616663', 'af88f921-2e07-48aa-a3e5-c556a2b2c223', 'af88f921-2e07-48aa-a3e5-c556a2b2c223'),
