      ('4acd430f-cceb-401c-95d6-40089cd99d4e', '2bcbf2b5-dbcd-41d0-ad80-29043388323e', 'description', 'Operational processes include reconciliation and verification activities to confirm system outputs, records, and data sets remain accurate and complete. These checks help identify discrepancies caused by processing errors, unauthorized changes, or system failures. Early detection reduces the impact of integrity issues and supports reliable operations.', '2026-04-06T15:17:13.707401', '2026-04-06T15:17:13.707401', 'af88f921-2e07-48aa-a3e5-c556a2b2c223', 'af88f921-2e07-48aa-a3e5-c556a2b2c223'),
      ('4ad21386-cfea-4e5d-a97a-badcde59a187', 'cebf28f2-379b-45d0-9105-5ff32aa851d4', 'implementation_guidance', '["Require documented approval before creating administrative accounts", "Assign least privilege access based on role requirements", "Maintain a register of all administrative users and privileges", "Review administrative account assignments periodically"]', '2026-04-07T18:29:03.504183', '2026-04-07T18:29:03.504183', '4add1867-32f4-4871-aa48-c683114039ce', '4add1867-32f4-4871-aa48-c683114039ce'),
      ('4b03f96d-cfb0-42f3-867c-3092d97c93e2', '3dcb224b-7d8e-4b70-9a81-9b726329608f', 'guidance', 'Use centralized request management processes or tools to track and manage all Data Principal rights requests.', '2026-04-07T18:00:21.828555', '2026-04-07T18:00:21.828555', '4add1867-32f4-4871-aa48-c683114039ce', '4add1867-32f4-4871-aa48-c683114039ce'),
      ('4b0955a7-c40a-47ff-b45f-8d0b38173974', 'a7ff3eaa-2d5c-4086-a546-ee387abaaa68', 'implementation_guidance', '["Create a centralized asset inventory covering hardware, software, virtual machines, and cloud services.", "Assign an owner responsible for each asset.", "Implement automated discovery tools to identify unmanaged or unknown assets.", "Review and reconcile asset inventory periodically against procurement and network discovery data."]', '2026-04-08T17:01:44.377349', '2026-04-09T04:25:49.713986', 'af88f921-2e07-48aa-a3e5-c556a2b2c223', 'af88f921-2e07-48aa-a3e5-c556a2b2c223'),
      ('4b454fae-dc5d-4827-936e-62f49e44ee4f', 'f97f2c1f-d952-4dcd-90f7-a0dc776efb71', 'implementation_guidance', '["Define approved processing purposes for each dataset", "Restrict system usage through role or purpose-based authorization", "Implement review checks before introducing new processing activities", "Monitor for unauthorized secondary data use"]', '2026-04-07T19:36:40.518698', '2026-04-07T19:36:40.518698', '4add1867-32f4-4871-aa48-c683114039ce', '4add1867-32f4-4871-aa48-c683114039ce'),
      ('4b9ff5d7-b602-4d14-a062-1bf661258a56', '9451f9a2-0949-4625-92cc-27ec042eb5c8', 'implementation_guidance', '["Define approved processing purposes in system design and data governance documentation", "Implement role-based access restrictions aligned with approved processing activities", "Conduct periodic audits to verify personal data is not used for unauthorized secondary purposes", "Require change management approval before introducing new processing purposes"]', '2026-04-07T18:00:21.732665', '2026-04-07T18:00:21.732665', '4add1867-32f4-4871-aa48-c683114039ce', '4add1867-32f4-4871-aa48-c683114039ce'),
      ('4c33d3db-8b39-4762-9226-17dd7db8d431', '220f68b1-0691-4f4b-8c16-8589bdc5cb6f', 'description', 'Develop a documented governance framework that defines how information security policies, standards, and procedures are created, maintained, and enforced across the organization. The framework ensures consistent oversight, accountability, and alignment between security activities and organizational risk management.', '2026-04-08T17:01:44.377349', '2026-04-09T04:25:49.713986', 'af88f921-2e07-48aa-a3e5-c556a2b2c223', 'af88f921-2e07-48aa-a3e5-c556a2b2c223'),
      ('4c784fa0-fb4f-4b0d-889b-d1f7e8345ca2', 'c17b7e42-fd63-4d57-92cb-6fadf30a244c', 'description', 'When vendor relationships end, the organization ensures that all vendor access is revoked and organizational data is returned or securely destroyed. This control prevents lingering access or uncontrolled retention of sensitive information by former service providers. Proper offboarding reduces long-term data exposure and unauthorized access risks.', '2026-04-06T15:17:31.086078', '2026-04-06T15:17:31.086078', 'af88f921-2e07-48aa-a3e5-c556a2b2c223', 'af88f921-2e07-48aa-a3e5-c556a2b2c223'),
      ('4cc23d17-2f2a-4602-ab1b-9292da13f566', 'b9606853-dc9c-4770-9eb7-ef3040acc600', 'implementation_guidance', '["Create a standardized risk register capturing risk description, owner, likelihood, impact, and treatment plan", "Assign accountable risk owners responsible for managing and updating each risk entry", "Integrate risks identified from audits, vulnerability scans, incidents, and vendor assessments", "Track risk status, mitigation progress, and residual risk ratings", "Conduct periodic reviews to validate accuracy and ensure risks remain current"]', '2026-04-06T15:17:03.773311', '2026-04-06T15:17:03.773311', 'af88f921-2e07-48aa-a3e5-c556a2b2c223', 'af88f921-2e07-48aa-a3e5-c556a2b2c223'),
      ('4ce168aa-f961-4bd5-9002-4cc140571cb4', '3523377d-20ab-440f-bf84-9ec6866a1118', 'description', 'Maintain a centralized risk register documenting identified information security risks, impact assessments, treatment decisions, and control mappings.', '2026-04-09T04:13:35.339189', '2026-04-09T04:25:49.713986', 'af88f921-2e07-48aa-a3e5-c556a2b2c223', 'af88f921-2e07-48aa-a3e5-c556a2b2c223'),
      ('4d2bf461-8298-43e4-82e4-e556090d0979', '807bbd34-3b97-40c7-a51f-ba040ddfca0e', 'name', 'Grievance Resolution Tracking', '2026-04-07T19:36:46.081445', '2026-04-07T19:36:46.081445', '4add1867-32f4-4871-aa48-c683114039ce', '4add1867-32f4-4871-aa48-c683114039ce'),
      ('4d57ce6c-77ee-460e-861d-0d1be1d553cf', 'a06a0924-7dbf-4fb5-8edd-a4d08b24253a', 'name', 'Enforce Multi-Factor Authentication for System and Remote Access', '2026-04-06T15:17:15.699148', '2026-04-06T15:17:15.699148', 'af88f921-2e07-48aa-a3e5-c556a2b2c223', 'af88f921-2e07-48aa-a3e5-c556a2b2c223'),
      ('4d7979c0-3a4e-4d57-b71f-8c7112e509b0', '8ee5d368-91b2-4618-ab70-44a0d4b176bd', 'implementation_guidance', '["Identify critical assets, systems, data types, and business processes within assessment scope", "Evaluate potential threats, vulnerabilities, and attack vectors affecting those assets", "Assess likelihood and impact using the organization\u2019s approved risk scoring methodology", "Document identified risks, recommended mitigation measures, and residual risk levels", "Present risk assessment results to management for review and remediation prioritization"]', '2026-04-06T15:17:04.435335', '2026-04-06T15:17:04.435335', 'af88f921-2e07-48aa-a3e5-c556a2b2c223', 'af88f921-2e07-48aa-a3e5-c556a2b2c223'),
      ('4e2b8740-8220-47bc-960f-e0baa8e0ed05', 'faa66b97-7296-48fb-a583-83937c6eea3d', 'description', 'Establish and enforce a documented acceptable use policy describing permitted and prohibited activities when using organizational systems and information resources. This ensures users understand their responsibilities and reduces misuse of organizational assets.', '2026-04-08T17:01:44.377349', '2026-04-09T04:25:49.713986', 'af88f921-2e07-48aa-a3e5-c556a2b2c223', 'af88f921-2e07-48aa-a3e5-c556a2b2c223'),
      ('4e5997dc-4d38-4438-8689-6b33cd2cdb8e', 'b4280d33-d460-4088-9ba0-b94e269dbcf9', 'guidance', 'Offer accessible complaint channels and define internal workflows for timely review and resolution of grievances.', '2026-04-07T18:00:22.189082', '2026-04-07T18:00:22.189082', '4add1867-32f4-4871-aa48-c683114039ce', '4add1867-32f4-4871-aa48-c683114039ce'),
      ('4e6dce5e-eb9c-46fa-a8f2-50f0055ba853', 'b7d07b5b-cd51-4967-8755-b00021647182', 'implementation_guidance', '["Identify personal data categories processed by the organization", "Define retention periods for each category", "Document legal or business justification for retention periods", "Review retention schedules periodically"]', '2026-04-07T18:44:28.74602', '2026-04-07T18:44:28.74602', '4add1867-32f4-4871-aa48-c683114039ce', '4add1867-32f4-4871-aa48-c683114039ce'),
      ('4e9ba9b6-2b72-4eb9-83a6-749e2be6716c', '03e55674-3c5f-494e-9189-f2d36adf5fd2', 'description', 'Organizations must implement a documented workflow to receive, verify, process, and respond to Data Principal rights requests.', '2026-04-07T18:44:26.510705', '2026-04-07T18:44:26.510705', '4add1867-32f4-4871-aa48-c683114039ce', '4add1867-32f4-4871-aa48-c683114039ce'),
      ('4edabd0e-5256-4ac1-bd58-816fc4346649', '18a440a3-1c20-4023-97c7-b4aeb2704144', 'implementation_guidance', '["Maintain records of processing activities involving personal data", "Store privacy policies, procedures, DPIAs, and control documentation in a centralized repository", "Ensure documentation is version controlled and regularly updated", "Retain compliance records for defined regulatory or internal retention periods"]', '2026-04-07T18:00:22.263824', '2026-04-07T18:00:22.263824', '4add1867-32f4-4871-aa48-c683114039ce', '4add1867-32f4-4871-aa48-c683114039ce'),
