      ('4fbd0142-44d3-4650-ac0f-569ee9bb1d66', '853f012c-e00c-4b6f-9002-edef9dffc7ba', 'description', 'Authentication events and access attempts are logged and analyzed to detect abnormal behavior such as repeated failed logins, unusual geographic access, or unauthorized privilege escalation. Automated alerts enable security teams to respond quickly to potential compromise or misuse of credentials.', '2026-04-06T15:17:17.596064', '2026-04-06T15:17:17.596064', 'af88f921-2e07-48aa-a3e5-c556a2b2c223', 'af88f921-2e07-48aa-a3e5-c556a2b2c223'),
