      ('5957244d-71c6-4e3b-a9db-c9a61740af13', 'c5261520-054b-4147-8cbf-7fa1c3999280', 'guidance', 'Notices should explain purpose, rights, grievance process, and contact details.', '2026-04-07T18:51:49.896325', '2026-04-07T18:51:49.896325', '4add1867-32f4-4871-aa48-c683114039ce', '4add1867-32f4-4871-aa48-c683114039ce'),
      ('59975054-98b5-47b8-aa64-d8c678fbdf65', '6face2da-ade4-431a-91e6-174b8d043f60', 'acceptance_criteria', '["Validation checks exist for personal data entry", "Periodic data accuracy reviews are conducted", "Data correction events are logged"]', '2026-04-07T19:13:14.244429', '2026-04-07T19:13:14.244429', '4add1867-32f4-4871-aa48-c683114039ce', '4add1867-32f4-4871-aa48-c683114039ce'),
      ('59b087bb-bf2c-4ec1-9f50-cc65f040a704', 'b5910f05-422d-415c-a1e9-e763cdcf2d39', 'name', 'Establish Vulnerability Scanning and Remediation Process', '2026-04-08T17:01:44.377349', '2026-04-09T04:25:49.713986', 'af88f921-2e07-48aa-a3e5-c556a2b2c223', 'af88f921-2e07-48aa-a3e5-c556a2b2c223'),
      ('59e9681b-9f14-4c3c-a89a-e915c74185d5', '23944a7a-86ca-44cf-9dda-646af9285768', 'description', 'Independent personnel periodically test and evaluate internal security controls to verify that they are functioning effectively and consistently. Independent assessments provide objective assurance beyond control owner attestations and help detect control failures or design weaknesses. Results are reported to management for remediation and oversight.', '2026-04-06T15:17:08.49601', '2026-04-06T15:17:08.49601', 'af88f921-2e07-48aa-a3e5-c556a2b2c223', 'af88f921-2e07-48aa-a3e5-c556a2b2c223'),
      ('5a5908e8-dfee-4c60-b458-e6ee8bfb3ea0', '6c0881a6-9815-4884-9fe2-eaf1e9409202', 'description', 'Ensure that personal data breaches are reported to regulators and affected Data Principals within required timelines where applicable. Maintain complete records of breach investigations, impact assessments, and notifications to demonstrate compliance with regulatory obligations.', '2026-04-07T18:00:22.034441', '2026-04-07T18:00:22.034441', '4add1867-32f4-4871-aa48-c683114039ce', '4add1867-32f4-4871-aa48-c683114039ce'),
      ('5a5c10fc-7b93-4771-a804-f6edb7d23958', '44e1eecf-e92c-4505-9d83-8535759d2bc3', 'name', 'Conduct Periodic User and Privileged Access Reviews', '2026-04-06T15:17:16.963868', '2026-04-06T15:17:16.963868', 'af88f921-2e07-48aa-a3e5-c556a2b2c223', 'af88f921-2e07-48aa-a3e5-c556a2b2c223'),
      ('5a673c38-495e-4ce0-8ad0-be944ba5694c', '3dcb224b-7d8e-4b70-9a81-9b726329608f', 'description', 'Establish procedures and systems to receive, track, and fulfill Data Principal rights requests such as access, correction, updating, and erasure of personal data. A structured workflow ensures requests are handled consistently, securely, and within required timelines. Proper handling supports regulatory compliance and individual rights protection.', '2026-04-07T18:00:21.828555', '2026-04-07T18:00:21.828555', '4add1867-32f4-4871-aa48-c683114039ce', '4add1867-32f4-4871-aa48-c683114039ce'),
      ('5a7da855-2bf7-4c57-a941-bcf03aaad333', 'ac52cfed-eb29-41ba-a1c6-87c627bbac6a', 'acceptance_criteria', '["Independent privacy audits are conducted periodically", "Audit reports are documented and reviewed", "Remediation plans are implemented for identified issues"]', '2026-04-07T19:36:47.46516', '2026-04-07T19:36:47.46516', '4add1867-32f4-4871-aa48-c683114039ce', '4add1867-32f4-4871-aa48-c683114039ce'),
      ('5ab954bb-550b-4a13-a458-23f54b06b054', '276d9ce2-0808-4ec2-b11d-9e6abc5b8cd1', 'name', 'Provide Mandatory Security Awareness and Responsibility Training', '2026-04-06T15:16:58.91588', '2026-04-06T15:16:58.91588', 'af88f921-2e07-48aa-a3e5-c556a2b2c223', 'af88f921-2e07-48aa-a3e5-c556a2b2c223'),
      ('5b4e7852-a415-4818-8b2d-b1549bc0b81b', '55fae56b-31b0-4dbd-947a-d67c9dcd6214', 'guidance', 'Create a cross‑functional governance body with authority to oversee ISMS strategy, risk management, and performance.', '2026-04-08T17:01:44.377349', '2026-04-09T04:25:49.713986', 'af88f921-2e07-48aa-a3e5-c556a2b2c223', 'af88f921-2e07-48aa-a3e5-c556a2b2c223'),
      ('5c05108f-138d-4caa-b80b-250e6392dd5a', '81683014-7616-4d66-b72c-cb2d6ad23155', 'name', 'Review Personal Data Collection for Minimization', '2026-04-07T19:13:14.301928', '2026-04-07T19:13:14.301928', '4add1867-32f4-4871-aa48-c683114039ce', '4add1867-32f4-4871-aa48-c683114039ce'),
      ('5c2bf96f-eafe-4d2e-a24a-9d51dd94cded', '71297127-54eb-4b99-b694-06b44a3b057f', 'name', 'Implement Centralized Security Log Collection and Retention', '2026-04-06T15:17:19.570031', '2026-04-06T15:17:19.570031', 'af88f921-2e07-48aa-a3e5-c556a2b2c223', 'af88f921-2e07-48aa-a3e5-c556a2b2c223'),
      ('5c3cd908-2347-4812-8428-87a220277f6c', '5b1e1d92-b20c-4b30-8a0f-e4ee83066f54', 'description', 'All changes to applications, infrastructure, configurations, and security components are formally documented through a centralized change management system before implementation. Each change record includes details such as purpose, scope, systems affected, risk classification, and planned implementation timeline. Maintaining traceable change documentation ensures accountability and reduces the risk of unauthorized or poorly understood modifications.', '2026-04-06T15:17:24.101379', '2026-04-06T15:17:24.101379', 'af88f921-2e07-48aa-a3e5-c556a2b2c223', 'af88f921-2e07-48aa-a3e5-c556a2b2c223'),
      ('5c58f76a-0460-49a9-81d5-77c6da503c7e', '276d9ce2-0808-4ec2-b11d-9e6abc5b8cd1', 'description', 'The organization provides regular security awareness training to ensure personnel understand their responsibilities in maintaining internal controls and protecting information assets. Training reinforces ethical behavior, security policies, and incident reporting obligations. This strengthens the overall control environment by ensuring personnel are equipped to recognize and prevent security risks.', '2026-04-06T15:16:58.91588', '2026-04-06T15:16:58.91588', 'af88f921-2e07-48aa-a3e5-c556a2b2c223', 'af88f921-2e07-48aa-a3e5-c556a2b2c223'),
      ('5cd42467-a44a-41f5-95a4-565c7a1e6a6b', 'd338d465-bb09-4904-a0fa-d92748897aea', 'guidance', 'Implement labeling standards across documents, systems, and data repositories.', '2026-04-08T17:01:44.377349', '2026-04-09T04:25:49.713986', 'af88f921-2e07-48aa-a3e5-c556a2b2c223', 'af88f921-2e07-48aa-a3e5-c556a2b2c223'),
      ('5cd7ebbe-0516-4fd1-854c-90ac1bc1d144', 'e570c128-6597-46ce-929d-51ffa4dbfa12', 'description', 'Restrict and monitor physical access to facilities, data centers, and sensitive operational areas to prevent unauthorized entry and potential compromise of systems or information assets.', '2026-04-08T17:01:44.377349', '2026-04-09T04:25:49.713986', 'af88f921-2e07-48aa-a3e5-c556a2b2c223', 'af88f921-2e07-48aa-a3e5-c556a2b2c223'),
      ('5cf92963-5502-4cef-a511-c67b5247231f', '44e1eecf-e92c-4505-9d83-8535759d2bc3', 'implementation_guidance', '["Perform access certification reviews at least quarterly for privileged access and annually for standard access.", "Provide system owners with reports listing all active users and assigned roles.", "Document approvals, modifications, and revocations resulting from each review cycle.", "Track completion of access reviews and escalate overdue certifications.", "Immediately remove access identified as unnecessary or excessive."]', '2026-04-06T15:17:16.963868', '2026-04-06T15:17:16.963868', 'af88f921-2e07-48aa-a3e5-c556a2b2c223', 'af88f921-2e07-48aa-a3e5-c556a2b2c223'),
      ('5d47c84c-77d2-4ecb-a119-5752d5b6744e', 'a9eecc25-906a-4134-a296-0431c5f15fe2', 'guidance', 'Document risk tolerance criteria and ensure they are approved by senior management and reviewed periodically. Align risk thresholds with business objectives and regulatory expectations.', '2026-04-06T15:17:03.088196', '2026-04-06T15:17:03.088196', 'af88f921-2e07-48aa-a3e5-c556a2b2c223', 'af88f921-2e07-48aa-a3e5-c556a2b2c223'),
      ('5d8c8f91-baff-453b-86c1-cf21fc93a36e', 'be04a4db-f834-43b4-b5d8-9f1c2ddd0970', 'guidance', 'Establish review frequencies based on vendor criticality and data sensitivity.', '2026-04-06T15:17:29.901758', '2026-04-06T15:17:29.901758', 'af88f921-2e07-48aa-a3e5-c556a2b2c223', 'af88f921-2e07-48aa-a3e5-c556a2b2c223'),
      ('5d9fcbbc-c3b5-4d2d-a297-a9fd7da262c5', '68c3432c-5f54-4aec-9b54-5974ece94a33', 'guidance', 'The ISMS scope must clearly state boundaries and applicability across the organization.', '2026-04-09T04:13:35.339189', '2026-04-09T04:25:49.713986', 'af88f921-2e07-48aa-a3e5-c556a2b2c223', 'af88f921-2e07-48aa-a3e5-c556a2b2c223'),
      ('5da2b288-af2a-423c-9061-2560fd4d14a5', 'ac52cfed-eb29-41ba-a1c6-87c627bbac6a', 'name', 'Independent Data Protection Audit', '2026-04-07T19:36:47.46516', '2026-04-07T19:36:47.46516', '4add1867-32f4-4871-aa48-c683114039ce', '4add1867-32f4-4871-aa48-c683114039ce'),
      ('5f194ee5-48cf-4446-8141-f6329aa497dc', 'e570c128-6597-46ce-929d-51ffa4dbfa12', 'name', 'Implement Physical Access Control Mechanisms', '2026-04-08T17:01:44.377349', '2026-04-09T04:25:49.713986', 'af88f921-2e07-48aa-a3e5-c556a2b2c223', 'af88f921-2e07-48aa-a3e5-c556a2b2c223'),
      ('5f241b84-dd7c-4e57-837d-976852b3c850', 'b4e9ec66-8d8c-4094-a8d6-fca76cedb459', 'description', 'Establish a formal governance structure responsible for oversight of personal data protection obligations under the DPDP Act. The structure defines accountability for data protection, including roles responsible for policy management, regulatory compliance, and oversight of data processing practices. This governance model ensures that personal data handling aligns with statutory requirements and organizational risk management practices.', '2026-04-07T18:00:21.677803', '2026-04-07T18:00:21.677803', '4add1867-32f4-4871-aa48-c683114039ce', '4add1867-32f4-4871-aa48-c683114039ce'),
      ('5f3ec22b-15e2-42aa-b615-17e300c813d2', '81933d25-9eee-4cf0-96a7-c34dac85fab7', 'guidance', 'Use modern cryptographic protocols such as TLS and enforce secure file transfer mechanisms.', '2026-04-08T17:01:44.377349', '2026-04-09T04:25:49.713986', 'af88f921-2e07-48aa-a3e5-c556a2b2c223', 'af88f921-2e07-48aa-a3e5-c556a2b2c223'),
      ('5fc3f069-8a3e-4663-b9d8-a5c39d47741d', 'e974a66b-6999-4076-beba-f6cda38d4955', 'name', 'Implement Physical Access Control for Secure Areas', '2026-04-08T17:01:44.377349', '2026-04-09T04:25:49.713986', 'af88f921-2e07-48aa-a3e5-c556a2b2c223', 'af88f921-2e07-48aa-a3e5-c556a2b2c223'),
      ('5fede2d3-474b-4aa7-9578-d66d3cc8a096', '74dcf5d1-22d1-4381-8fe3-6ee797a4de75', 'description', 'Define and enforce baseline configuration and system hardening standards for servers, endpoints, network devices, and cloud resources. Hardened configurations reduce attack surface and limit exploitation opportunities by removing unnecessary services and insecure settings.', '2026-04-08T17:01:44.377349', '2026-04-09T04:25:49.713986', 'af88f921-2e07-48aa-a3e5-c556a2b2c223', 'af88f921-2e07-48aa-a3e5-c556a2b2c223'),
      ('602587ac-345d-43ca-aa1b-33046559f33b', 'cb1fecf9-c6a8-44f9-b2c7-def42e267146', 'acceptance_criteria', '["Periodic compliance reviews are conducted", "Findings and remediation actions are documented", "Management receives compliance status reports"]', '2026-04-07T19:36:48.961134', '2026-04-07T19:36:48.961134', '4add1867-32f4-4871-aa48-c683114039ce', '4add1867-32f4-4871-aa48-c683114039ce'),
      ('60cc2b12-7128-42bf-8473-c7cd08d19e13', '1996d6fb-40fe-4981-a566-62b52b1f176e', 'description', 'Ensure contracts with third-party processors define responsibilities for protecting personal data and complying with DPDP requirements. Contractual clauses establish enforceable obligations regarding security safeguards, breach notification, and permitted processing activities.', '2026-04-07T18:00:22.079337', '2026-04-07T18:00:22.079337', '4add1867-32f4-4871-aa48-c683114039ce', '4add1867-32f4-4871-aa48-c683114039ce'),
      ('6110e614-8341-4f5f-8f3b-9b278b6b5880', '8184b1be-9a06-4f2d-9d2b-e178aab18542', 'implementation_guidance', '["Create a centralized register of personal data processing activities", "Record the legal basis for each activity", "Require privacy review before initiating new processing", "Update records when purposes or legal bases change"]', '2026-04-07T18:51:46.984959', '2026-04-07T18:51:46.984959', '4add1867-32f4-4871-aa48-c683114039ce', '4add1867-32f4-4871-aa48-c683114039ce'),
      ('611cff2e-7990-402d-914c-28d9958e497f', '78949283-ef74-4348-9f54-59a6e1684de3', 'guidance', 'DPIAs help identify and mitigate privacy risks prior to implementing new processing operations.', '2026-04-07T19:36:46.773235', '2026-04-07T19:36:46.773235', '4add1867-32f4-4871-aa48-c683114039ce', '4add1867-32f4-4871-aa48-c683114039ce'),
      ('6120dc1e-02a7-47e6-ba03-e182d714df7d', '5006dd25-c0e4-41d2-8559-550f8faebee8', 'guidance', 'Account recovery processes should validate user identity and limit the validity of reset links or tokens.', '2026-04-07T18:29:03.452906', '2026-04-07T18:29:03.452906', '4add1867-32f4-4871-aa48-c683114039ce', '4add1867-32f4-4871-aa48-c683114039ce'),
      ('61d4ef5c-f49e-4dfb-b52a-336b4ba6dba1', '4cf09354-eac7-4e30-8747-1c93fee128cc', 'name', 'Conduct Periodic Access Rights Review', '2026-04-08T17:01:44.377349', '2026-04-09T04:25:49.713986', 'af88f921-2e07-48aa-a3e5-c556a2b2c223', 'af88f921-2e07-48aa-a3e5-c556a2b2c223'),
      ('61d5cef9-cd84-4855-9223-1e574769f1e7', 'e23914b9-c312-4e9b-ba01-bae41134a4e3', 'name', 'Track and Remediate Detected Security Vulnerabilities', '2026-04-06T15:17:22.864221', '2026-04-06T15:17:22.864221', 'af88f921-2e07-48aa-a3e5-c556a2b2c223', 'af88f921-2e07-48aa-a3e5-c556a2b2c223'),
      ('62a9916c-8f6b-4e04-adf8-6ba677e1c6b8', '86c070c0-91b7-43ff-9c60-259e6df53c28', 'name', 'Implement Verifiable Consent Capture Mechanisms', '2026-04-07T18:00:21.755596', '2026-04-07T18:00:21.755596', '4add1867-32f4-4871-aa48-c683114039ce', '4add1867-32f4-4871-aa48-c683114039ce'),
      ('62d8e63c-c762-4b30-a01b-10f288d85482', '10e512b8-6796-4df8-a914-751cddc6e499', 'implementation_guidance', '["Identify applicable laws, regulations, contractual clauses, and industry standards affecting information security and data protection.", "Maintain a compliance obligations register linking each obligation to responsible owners and implemented controls.", "Map obligations to relevant policies, procedures, and technical safeguards.", "Review and update the register at least annually or when regulatory or contractual changes occur."]', '2026-04-08T17:01:44.377349', '2026-04-09T04:25:49.713986', 'af88f921-2e07-48aa-a3e5-c556a2b2c223', 'af88f921-2e07-48aa-a3e5-c556a2b2c223'),
      ('6385990d-9b57-4477-bca9-0215488ab277', '9dcafd31-fd62-45ad-8230-5b8241c32421', 'guidance', 'Adopt a defense-in-depth approach that combines identity, encryption, and system hardening controls across all environments handling personal data.', '2026-04-07T18:00:21.970387', '2026-04-07T18:00:21.970387', '4add1867-32f4-4871-aa48-c683114039ce', '4add1867-32f4-4871-aa48-c683114039ce'),
      ('638695c7-bdf5-452f-82a4-9e2055fc4e93', 'daae86b7-1c1d-4e34-90ad-f7da4eaa49df', 'description', 'Accounts exhibiting suspicious behavior or extended inactivity are automatically locked or disabled to prevent unauthorized use. This control helps limit opportunities for attackers to exploit dormant or compromised credentials while ensuring rapid containment of potential access abuse.', '2026-04-06T15:17:18.943177', '2026-04-06T15:17:18.943177', 'af88f921-2e07-48aa-a3e5-c556a2b2c223', 'af88f921-2e07-48aa-a3e5-c556a2b2c223'),
      ('63c54c43-6bc4-4ba9-b026-6125ab2beaee', '21c26368-94f0-4cf5-bbc2-0e5711613be3', 'guidance', 'Use qualified internal audit teams or independent external assessors to review data protection practices regularly.', '2026-04-07T18:00:22.237708', '2026-04-07T18:00:22.237708', '4add1867-32f4-4871-aa48-c683114039ce', '4add1867-32f4-4871-aa48-c683114039ce'),
      ('63fb96a4-9a3c-4408-b10e-e75485760345', '4703eb9d-b0c7-4ce8-aca2-0de8e038a061', 'name', 'Limit Data Collection Fields', '2026-04-07T18:51:51.549195', '2026-04-07T18:51:51.549195', '4add1867-32f4-4871-aa48-c683114039ce', '4add1867-32f4-4871-aa48-c683114039ce'),
      ('6467dd66-5bdb-4985-ab4a-70115f930dfc', '8ee5d368-91b2-4618-ab70-44a0d4b176bd', 'guidance', 'Perform comprehensive risk assessments at least annually and when significant changes occur in technology, infrastructure, or regulatory obligations.', '2026-04-06T15:17:04.435335', '2026-04-06T15:17:04.435335', 'af88f921-2e07-48aa-a3e5-c556a2b2c223', 'af88f921-2e07-48aa-a3e5-c556a2b2c223'),
      ('646bd388-c946-45b4-b238-e3f05d6559ca', 'ab57aba8-5084-4083-a655-c0f3e18e502b', 'guidance', 'Document cloud usage policies and review provider capabilities before adoption.', '2026-04-08T17:01:44.377349', '2026-04-09T04:25:49.713986', 'af88f921-2e07-48aa-a3e5-c556a2b2c223', 'af88f921-2e07-48aa-a3e5-c556a2b2c223'),
      ('64eb076d-ffc2-416b-9def-4e1e4929efb0', '1ec5e73a-a759-428b-b6a1-d4da25595173', 'description', 'Implement mechanisms to identify when personal data belongs to a child and ensure verifiable parental or guardian consent is obtained before processing. This prevents unlawful collection or use of children''s personal data and supports compliance with DPDP obligations.', '2026-04-07T18:00:22.14531', '2026-04-07T18:00:22.14531', '4add1867-32f4-4871-aa48-c683114039ce', '4add1867-32f4-4871-aa48-c683114039ce'),
      ('6533ec45-19ce-47c3-8a83-4990e56cfb09', '18a440a3-1c20-4023-97c7-b4aeb2704144', 'description', 'Maintain documented evidence demonstrating compliance with DPDP obligations, including policies, processing records, procedures, and control evidence. Proper documentation supports regulatory inspections and ensures transparency in personal data management practices.', '2026-04-07T18:00:22.263824', '2026-04-07T18:00:22.263824', '4add1867-32f4-4871-aa48-c683114039ce', '4add1867-32f4-4871-aa48-c683114039ce'),
      ('65656eaf-a3db-4850-9893-3e3efa9ff2d4', '220f68b1-0691-4f4b-8c16-8589bdc5cb6f', 'name', 'Define and Maintain Information Security Governance Framework', '2026-04-08T17:01:44.377349', '2026-04-09T04:25:49.713986', 'af88f921-2e07-48aa-a3e5-c556a2b2c223', 'af88f921-2e07-48aa-a3e5-c556a2b2c223'),
      ('65ea2249-71fb-4f9c-8353-3cec8f20b6b7', '66e2d32a-d929-44a3-bc0e-8846e4a55cde', 'name', 'Protect and Restrict Access to Security Monitoring Infrastructure', '2026-04-06T15:17:23.493885', '2026-04-06T15:17:23.493885', 'af88f921-2e07-48aa-a3e5-c556a2b2c223', 'af88f921-2e07-48aa-a3e5-c556a2b2c223'),
      ('663ebd33-a797-4d44-bcba-2d55640d9c3c', '644898fc-e846-415f-b288-8d044e203c65', 'name', 'Integrate Security Requirements into Project Lifecycle', '2026-04-08T17:01:44.377349', '2026-04-09T04:25:49.713986', 'af88f921-2e07-48aa-a3e5-c556a2b2c223', 'af88f921-2e07-48aa-a3e5-c556a2b2c223'),
      ('66a2080a-7343-4e82-8b47-58ec47bcca81', '4db2d477-80ee-458e-91dd-1bd4748d5e08', 'acceptance_criteria', '["Retention schedule exists for all personal data categories", "Expired data is deleted or anonymized", "Retention policies are reviewed periodically"]', '2026-04-07T19:13:14.349303', '2026-04-07T19:13:14.349303', '4add1867-32f4-4871-aa48-c683114039ce', '4add1867-32f4-4871-aa48-c683114039ce'),
      ('66d3c102-430e-4093-83f1-0c9313fbcf53', '7ab5c678-2e60-4f36-b832-e4693593e6a2', 'description', 'Define formal procedures for communicating security incidents, control failures, and potential breaches to internal stakeholders and, when required, external parties. Timely and accurate communication supports effective response, regulatory compliance, and coordination across teams.', '2026-04-06T15:17:01.705747', '2026-04-06T15:17:01.705747', 'af88f921-2e07-48aa-a3e5-c556a2b2c223', 'af88f921-2e07-48aa-a3e5-c556a2b2c223'),
      ('6710286b-e045-43ca-939f-8002690f6460', 'faa66b97-7296-48fb-a583-83937c6eea3d', 'name', 'Define and Enforce Acceptable Use Policy for Information Assets', '2026-04-08T17:01:44.377349', '2026-04-09T04:25:49.713986', 'af88f921-2e07-48aa-a3e5-c556a2b2c223', 'af88f921-2e07-48aa-a3e5-c556a2b2c223'),
