      ('6a14ddb4-ad70-4555-a124-178aff7bf505', 'a06a0924-7dbf-4fb5-8edd-a4d08b24253a', 'guidance', 'Deploy MFA through an identity provider or authentication platform supporting hardware tokens, mobile authenticators, or biometric factors.', '2026-04-06T15:17:15.699148', '2026-04-06T15:17:15.699148', 'af88f921-2e07-48aa-a3e5-c556a2b2c223', 'af88f921-2e07-48aa-a3e5-c556a2b2c223'),
      ('6a5cc3bf-f9d6-4efd-a979-946de88410a9', '7848d86f-e632-46d8-84c5-6ea2e7b56da0', 'implementation_guidance', '["Provide channels for submitting rights requests", "Verify identity of requestors before processing requests", "Track request status in a centralized system", "Document response timelines and outcomes"]', '2026-04-07T19:13:14.190621', '2026-04-07T19:13:14.190621', '4add1867-32f4-4871-aa48-c683114039ce', '4add1867-32f4-4871-aa48-c683114039ce'),
      ('6b060f7f-3eaf-44b1-a70b-914c137854fa', '163f66fa-6159-4cb5-ba3f-fa587b8fd24a', 'guidance', 'Develop a set of measurable security KPIs and KRIs aligned with organizational risks and control objectives and review them regularly.', '2026-04-06T15:17:09.124957', '2026-04-06T15:17:09.124957', 'af88f921-2e07-48aa-a3e5-c556a2b2c223', 'af88f921-2e07-48aa-a3e5-c556a2b2c223'),
      ('6b63e545-b3e3-4510-b98a-caa1264caa66', '66d1ecd9-9c4c-434b-97fd-307c901116eb', 'guidance', 'Deliver periodic security awareness campaigns and role-based training for personnel handling sensitive systems or data.', '2026-04-08T17:01:44.377349', '2026-04-09T04:25:49.713986', 'af88f921-2e07-48aa-a3e5-c556a2b2c223', 'af88f921-2e07-48aa-a3e5-c556a2b2c223'),
      ('6b70ad36-7ce7-447a-a1a3-ac6cb8b62882', 'dad63953-4847-475a-a7aa-ec2f042b5bfa', 'guidance', 'The processing record should support regulatory inspections and internal compliance monitoring.', '2026-04-07T18:44:30.660547', '2026-04-07T18:44:30.660547', '4add1867-32f4-4871-aa48-c683114039ce', '4add1867-32f4-4871-aa48-c683114039ce'),
      ('6bc9b785-62e9-451e-be82-0b92697c4fea', 'a9eecc25-906a-4134-a296-0431c5f15fe2', 'description', 'The organization formally defines its risk appetite and tolerance levels for information security and operational risks. This establishes clear thresholds for acceptable risk and guides decision-making when evaluating security threats, vulnerabilities, and mitigation priorities. Documented risk tolerance ensures consistent treatment of risks across systems, processes, and third‑party relationships.', '2026-04-06T15:17:03.088196', '2026-04-06T15:17:03.088196', 'af88f921-2e07-48aa-a3e5-c556a2b2c223', 'af88f921-2e07-48aa-a3e5-c556a2b2c223'),
      ('6bd10577-f983-4b6b-bcd0-82857b0b813b', 'cc44ae6f-57ae-45a0-8fb9-9272f015a19d', 'implementation_guidance', '["Define datasets requiring accuracy validation", "Run periodic data validation checks", "Correct or flag inaccurate records", "Document data correction actions"]', '2026-04-07T19:36:42.916279', '2026-04-07T19:36:42.916279', '4add1867-32f4-4871-aa48-c683114039ce', '4add1867-32f4-4871-aa48-c683114039ce'),
      ('6be8c362-ea9c-45ac-924a-d4e5e302309f', '4e2bb384-902c-4714-866f-9ffb247e3311', 'name', 'Implement Segregation of Duties for Sensitive Activities', '2026-04-08T17:01:44.377349', '2026-04-09T04:25:49.713986', 'af88f921-2e07-48aa-a3e5-c556a2b2c223', 'af88f921-2e07-48aa-a3e5-c556a2b2c223'),
      ('6ca87aab-9f81-4bae-81c2-59fb72b5c605', '037846f7-1941-4d75-8ff7-a8cbbe770ca3', 'name', 'Implement Information Security Awareness and Training Program', '2026-04-09T04:20:31.950465', '2026-04-09T04:25:49.713986', 'af88f921-2e07-48aa-a3e5-c556a2b2c223', 'af88f921-2e07-48aa-a3e5-c556a2b2c223'),
      ('6cbdb274-5911-4e67-9fdb-a0eac3336a88', 'd338d465-bb09-4904-a0fa-d92748897aea', 'name', 'Enforce Information Labelling and Handling Procedures', '2026-04-08T17:01:44.377349', '2026-04-09T04:25:49.713986', 'af88f921-2e07-48aa-a3e5-c556a2b2c223', 'af88f921-2e07-48aa-a3e5-c556a2b2c223'),
      ('6cd85075-9112-49ed-902d-e6a78f6e8b6c', '4599995a-e91f-4505-9431-bdbd8f2b1654', 'description', 'Critical system operations are structured to ensure that no single individual can initiate, approve, and execute sensitive actions without oversight. Segregation of duties reduces the risk of fraud, misuse of privileged access, and unauthorized system changes. This control helps ensure accountability and oversight for high-impact activities.', '2026-04-06T15:17:11.825755', '2026-04-06T15:17:11.825755', 'af88f921-2e07-48aa-a3e5-c556a2b2c223', 'af88f921-2e07-48aa-a3e5-c556a2b2c223'),
      ('6d5d4683-7208-4329-9dfb-cadc9a71bf20', '964773c6-cd11-463e-b9ce-0dfbd93ec14c', 'guidance', 'Integrate asset discovery and inventory processes with monitoring platforms to ensure all relevant assets are included in control monitoring activities.', '2026-04-06T15:17:09.802343', '2026-04-06T15:17:09.802343', 'af88f921-2e07-48aa-a3e5-c556a2b2c223', 'af88f921-2e07-48aa-a3e5-c556a2b2c223'),
      ('6de681a9-0160-4df0-a52c-15b0a30925fc', '6be7389d-f6f8-429a-8ca1-8aefb8303cbb', 'implementation_guidance', '["Define risk identification and assessment processes.", "Establish risk scoring criteria for likelihood and impact.", "Define risk acceptance and escalation thresholds.", "Document and approve the methodology."]', '2026-04-09T04:13:35.339189', '2026-04-09T04:25:49.713986', 'af88f921-2e07-48aa-a3e5-c556a2b2c223', 'af88f921-2e07-48aa-a3e5-c556a2b2c223'),
      ('6ecd7870-72b1-4097-9ef7-3627a85ee77c', '10e512b8-6796-4df8-a914-751cddc6e499', 'guidance', 'Create a centralized compliance obligations register mapped to relevant systems, processes, and control owners.', '2026-04-08T17:01:44.377349', '2026-04-09T04:25:49.713986', 'af88f921-2e07-48aa-a3e5-c556a2b2c223', 'af88f921-2e07-48aa-a3e5-c556a2b2c223'),
      ('6fcb3fe1-87bf-4030-bc87-3dfefea86bc3', 'ab045248-5b25-4404-9cfe-e640e6e27508', 'acceptance_criteria', '["All personal data processing activities have a documented lawful basis", "Processing register is maintained and reviewed periodically", "New processing initiatives undergo privacy or legal review"]', '2026-04-07T18:44:23.712969', '2026-04-07T18:44:23.712969', '4add1867-32f4-4871-aa48-c683114039ce', '4add1867-32f4-4871-aa48-c683114039ce'),
      ('6fdcf4f5-5523-44ad-8780-e40700bbef43', '4cf09354-eac7-4e30-8747-1c93fee128cc', 'implementation_guidance', '["Conduct quarterly or semiannual access reviews for critical systems and sensitive data.", "Provide system owners with reports listing current users and privilege levels.", "Require formal confirmation, modification, or revocation of each user''s access.", "Track remediation actions and revoke unnecessary or outdated privileges."]', '2026-04-08T17:01:44.377349', '2026-04-09T04:25:49.713986', 'af88f921-2e07-48aa-a3e5-c556a2b2c223', 'af88f921-2e07-48aa-a3e5-c556a2b2c223'),
      ('6ffade05-61bf-4d02-bc1c-693ba45c15fa', '573acf45-ec9f-4635-a188-8c7229490619', 'name', 'Implement Data Collection Validation Controls', '2026-04-07T18:29:03.550262', '2026-04-07T18:29:03.550262', '4add1867-32f4-4871-aa48-c683114039ce', '4add1867-32f4-4871-aa48-c683114039ce'),
      ('700367dc-9741-423e-b713-e605fb3d5afc', 'f436e044-b778-4cfa-affc-0d0972c4ea9d', 'description', 'Define and document retention periods for different categories of personal data in accordance with business and legal requirements.', '2026-04-07T18:58:54.799828', '2026-04-07T18:58:54.799828', '4add1867-32f4-4871-aa48-c683114039ce', '4add1867-32f4-4871-aa48-c683114039ce'),
      ('7022ccdf-11b5-43f6-85fa-cf2165b6b939', '2f19fa6b-3132-4df7-bf1e-f06fa4c3fe1b', 'guidance', 'Records should be updated whenever processing activities change.', '2026-04-07T18:58:56.704966', '2026-04-07T18:58:56.704966', '4add1867-32f4-4871-aa48-c683114039ce', '4add1867-32f4-4871-aa48-c683114039ce'),
      ('7050ce22-ea2d-40f7-9c3f-5aa2e28e171f', '873c5dd9-14e1-44a3-aea2-e14f3cb3bef6', 'description', 'The organization performs background verification and security vetting for employees and contractors prior to granting access to systems or sensitive data. Screening helps identify potential risks related to trustworthiness and suitability for sensitive roles. This process reduces the likelihood of insider threats and misuse of privileged access.', '2026-04-06T15:16:58.546367', '2026-04-06T15:16:58.546367', 'af88f921-2e07-48aa-a3e5-c556a2b2c223', 'af88f921-2e07-48aa-a3e5-c556a2b2c223'),
      ('706a1f4e-6db2-4def-9a04-1af50e4bde0b', 'af2212ca-5633-4b3d-bf2d-5631044687ee', 'guidance', 'Document management must address version control, access protection, and retention.', '2026-04-09T04:13:35.339189', '2026-04-09T04:25:49.713986', 'af88f921-2e07-48aa-a3e5-c556a2b2c223', 'af88f921-2e07-48aa-a3e5-c556a2b2c223'),
      ('70df7472-4359-407c-869d-938c91653275', 'af3b8516-e554-4a41-ae04-a47cd9de5b89', 'implementation_guidance', '["Define role-based screening criteria including identity verification, employment history, and criminal background checks where permitted.", "Ensure screening processes comply with local employment and privacy laws.", "Document and retain verification results securely within HR records.", "Require completion of screening prior to granting system or facility access."]', '2026-04-08T17:01:44.377349', '2026-04-09T04:25:49.713986', 'af88f921-2e07-48aa-a3e5-c556a2b2c223', 'af88f921-2e07-48aa-a3e5-c556a2b2c223'),
      ('7174db3a-0510-43b2-a5bb-7a9a5425d3b2', '4c036014-d4b9-4537-9e09-baea8f91def6', 'description', 'Identify and document competence requirements for personnel performing roles affecting information security.', '2026-04-09T04:13:35.339189', '2026-04-09T04:25:49.713986', 'af88f921-2e07-48aa-a3e5-c556a2b2c223', 'af88f921-2e07-48aa-a3e5-c556a2b2c223'),
      ('71824dc0-2df8-430e-a505-538806ccc829', 'b61a8edb-cb85-4500-814b-607c2ce6fd0e', 'acceptance_criteria', '["Requests are logged and tracked", "Requests are fulfilled within defined timelines"]', '2026-04-07T18:58:51.742261', '2026-04-07T18:58:51.742261', '4add1867-32f4-4871-aa48-c683114039ce', '4add1867-32f4-4871-aa48-c683114039ce'),
      ('71f0d02a-943e-4e5d-87e9-688a5a7df2b9', '95f9d4c4-0d22-48f1-a5aa-4fde70eba35f', 'guidance', 'Use cloud-native or third-party monitoring tools to maintain visibility into cloud environments.', '2026-04-08T17:01:44.377349', '2026-04-09T04:25:49.713986', 'af88f921-2e07-48aa-a3e5-c556a2b2c223', 'af88f921-2e07-48aa-a3e5-c556a2b2c223'),
      ('724d5f6f-bfa8-4b33-b266-c9cc3ee791e7', '5b5296da-9902-4c5d-8232-b601ab5f1852', 'implementation_guidance', '["Create a structured inventory of all personal data processing activities", "Document purpose, lawful basis, data categories, and processing systems", "Record involved data processors and cross\u2011border transfers where applicable", "Review and update the processing register periodically"]', '2026-04-07T19:36:39.573896', '2026-04-07T19:36:39.573896', '4add1867-32f4-4871-aa48-c683114039ce', '4add1867-32f4-4871-aa48-c683114039ce'),
      ('725dc1b1-18ee-47ef-aea2-dd2f8f2118b1', '81683014-7616-4d66-b72c-cb2d6ad23155', 'acceptance_criteria', '["Data collection points are periodically reviewed", "Unnecessary personal data fields are removed", "Justification exists for retained data fields"]', '2026-04-07T19:13:14.301928', '2026-04-07T19:13:14.301928', '4add1867-32f4-4871-aa48-c683114039ce', '4add1867-32f4-4871-aa48-c683114039ce'),
      ('72d33d1a-56f6-4129-9295-87e3b137d975', 'e3cc508d-4eb4-43a6-a93a-d8e820ced1a9', 'description', 'Limit access to systems containing personal data based on least privilege and role-based authorization.', '2026-04-07T19:13:14.44361', '2026-04-07T19:13:14.44361', '4add1867-32f4-4871-aa48-c683114039ce', '4add1867-32f4-4871-aa48-c683114039ce'),
      ('72fd2e1b-c352-4e4c-b91d-b31f6640ec3a', 'd338d465-bb09-4904-a0fa-d92748897aea', 'description', 'Ensure that classified information is clearly labelled and handled according to defined protection requirements. Proper labeling helps users recognize sensitivity levels and apply appropriate safeguards to prevent accidental exposure or misuse.', '2026-04-08T17:01:44.377349', '2026-04-09T04:25:49.713986', 'af88f921-2e07-48aa-a3e5-c556a2b2c223', 'af88f921-2e07-48aa-a3e5-c556a2b2c223'),
      ('73081101-4c83-4d24-bf7c-8d0d9e2d162c', '80ca07cf-eb89-4294-aa8e-938b8abb0858', 'acceptance_criteria', '["A centralized registry of personal data processing applications exists", "Each application entry identifies owner, processing purpose, and data categories", "The inventory is periodically reviewed and updated"]', '2026-04-07T19:19:31.394795', '2026-04-07T19:19:31.394795', '4add1867-32f4-4871-aa48-c683114039ce', '4add1867-32f4-4871-aa48-c683114039ce'),
      ('73202e90-a5e5-4d0e-9ed9-c33a0928009a', '8d4080da-ac23-4efe-a90e-4b00af17484d', 'name', 'Define and Communicate Information Security Roles and Responsibilities', '2026-04-08T17:01:44.377349', '2026-04-09T04:25:49.713986', 'af88f921-2e07-48aa-a3e5-c556a2b2c223', 'af88f921-2e07-48aa-a3e5-c556a2b2c223'),
      ('73337fcd-bf75-4786-b4a6-f66af543f1fd', '762df5cb-f8e9-41b5-92fe-564e8b7f33df', 'implementation_guidance', '["Create a Statement of Applicability listing all Annex A controls and indicating whether each is applicable or excluded", "Document justification for excluding any control from the ISMS", "Link each applicable control to risks identified in the risk assessment and the implemented treatment measures", "Review and update the SoA following major risk assessments, control changes, or audit findings"]', '2026-04-09T04:20:31.791874', '2026-04-09T04:25:49.713986', 'af88f921-2e07-48aa-a3e5-c556a2b2c223', 'af88f921-2e07-48aa-a3e5-c556a2b2c223'),
      ('734da465-2f9e-4ce4-a92d-05894e6a8816', 'f5b150f5-007f-405a-9eae-35a6c94ca794', 'guidance', 'Schedule recurring privacy compliance assessments and incorporate regulatory change monitoring into review cycles.', '2026-04-07T18:00:22.319436', '2026-04-07T18:00:22.319436', '4add1867-32f4-4871-aa48-c683114039ce', '4add1867-32f4-4871-aa48-c683114039ce'),
      ('743a585b-1ea3-42b4-ace6-27b96a1bcee1', '1967551b-0805-4cb9-b86e-3cf0b5d5b68a', 'name', 'Monitor and Measure Information Security Performance', '2026-04-09T04:20:32.033669', '2026-04-09T04:25:49.713986', 'af88f921-2e07-48aa-a3e5-c556a2b2c223', 'af88f921-2e07-48aa-a3e5-c556a2b2c223'),
      ('74feb584-5c37-4de7-b8a3-c918623f6990', '736fd12f-02d8-4476-ad1f-f2a546cf44f6', 'description', 'Third-party vendors are granted only the minimum level of access necessary to perform contracted services, and their activities are monitored. Limiting and monitoring vendor access reduces the risk of unauthorized actions, data exposure, or compromise originating from vendor accounts or integrations. This control ensures vendor access aligns with least privilege principles.', '2026-04-06T15:17:30.493929', '2026-04-06T15:17:30.493929', 'af88f921-2e07-48aa-a3e5-c556a2b2c223', 'af88f921-2e07-48aa-a3e5-c556a2b2c223'),
      ('7525f181-5e21-4094-8b69-b65209744e37', 'fcd799bd-5663-4dbe-ac53-5eee7f57d15f', 'description', 'Ensure changes to the ISMS are systematically planned, evaluated, and documented before implementation.', '2026-04-09T04:13:35.339189', '2026-04-09T04:25:49.713986', 'af88f921-2e07-48aa-a3e5-c556a2b2c223', 'af88f921-2e07-48aa-a3e5-c556a2b2c223'),
      ('760faea5-e562-4212-b658-d0d86a15f3af', 'ba09e807-6318-4c6c-9f62-e2c8c1ce0b48', 'implementation_guidance', '["Integrate HR or personnel onboarding processes with identity management systems for automated account provisioning.", "Automatically disable or delete user accounts when employment or contract relationships end.", "Enforce standardized naming conventions and unique identifiers for user accounts.", "Maintain audit trails for account creation, modification, and deletion activities.", "Regularly reconcile active accounts with HR or contractor records."]', '2026-04-06T15:17:15.037142', '2026-04-06T15:17:15.037142', 'af88f921-2e07-48aa-a3e5-c556a2b2c223', 'af88f921-2e07-48aa-a3e5-c556a2b2c223'),
      ('767b7cb0-2046-4aca-833c-7b241032064d', 'dad63953-4847-475a-a7aa-ec2f042b5bfa', 'description', 'Organizations must maintain documented records describing categories of personal data processed, purposes, storage locations, processors, and safeguards.', '2026-04-07T18:44:30.660547', '2026-04-07T18:44:30.660547', '4add1867-32f4-4871-aa48-c683114039ce', '4add1867-32f4-4871-aa48-c683114039ce'),
      ('76be0494-d0e7-4580-b86c-d400d71ab5b7', '2b2927c1-14a9-49b3-ae30-5db30f52e9f0', 'name', 'Publish and Maintain Privacy Notice', '2026-04-07T19:36:41.844271', '2026-04-07T19:36:41.844271', '4add1867-32f4-4871-aa48-c683114039ce', '4add1867-32f4-4871-aa48-c683114039ce'),
      ('76cdf776-b526-456d-9271-424798702514', 'c9fc9cfd-5fa4-4642-a595-26b42e4941e6', 'name', 'Establish and Maintain Information Security Governance Charter', '2026-04-06T15:16:57.207266', '2026-04-06T15:16:57.207266', 'af88f921-2e07-48aa-a3e5-c556a2b2c223', 'af88f921-2e07-48aa-a3e5-c556a2b2c223'),
      ('77447227-ba00-4f01-9ddd-0004484b3595', '478bf708-7964-4103-aab4-56ea6eb6d2ee', 'guidance', 'Create a retention schedule aligned with legal obligations and business needs and review it periodically.', '2026-04-07T18:00:21.927998', '2026-04-07T18:00:21.927998', '4add1867-32f4-4871-aa48-c683114039ce', '4add1867-32f4-4871-aa48-c683114039ce'),
      ('774d3d1a-d782-4512-bace-c977f232cdd0', 'df0923d3-14cb-400e-9d2d-70bfecd7f022', 'implementation_guidance', '["Define contractual clauses covering data protection, confidentiality, and acceptable use.", "Require timely breach notification and incident cooperation obligations.", "Specify security control requirements aligned with organizational policies.", "Track compliance with contractual security obligations through periodic reviews."]', '2026-04-08T17:01:44.377349', '2026-04-09T04:25:49.713986', 'af88f921-2e07-48aa-a3e5-c556a2b2c223', 'af88f921-2e07-48aa-a3e5-c556a2b2c223'),
      ('775a0586-2bd0-4482-b342-c0a69092e33b', 'c17b7e42-fd63-4d57-92cb-6fadf30a244c', 'name', 'Execute Secure Vendor Offboarding and Data Return Procedures', '2026-04-06T15:17:31.086078', '2026-04-06T15:17:31.086078', 'af88f921-2e07-48aa-a3e5-c556a2b2c223', 'af88f921-2e07-48aa-a3e5-c556a2b2c223'),
      ('777c99bc-47b8-4bf7-81d7-1643c10d0d21', 'd2081300-717e-4950-b793-28a3c7fb7116', 'name', 'Define Organizational Context for Information Security', '2026-04-09T04:13:35.339189', '2026-04-09T04:25:49.713986', 'af88f921-2e07-48aa-a3e5-c556a2b2c223', 'af88f921-2e07-48aa-a3e5-c556a2b2c223'),
      ('784dd7c5-f540-4fdb-b10f-aa6764e4bac3', 'e89d79ab-0dcf-4385-9c5f-1458924de543', 'guidance', 'Training should address handling of personal data, breach reporting, and regulatory obligations.', '2026-04-07T19:13:14.549828', '2026-04-07T19:13:14.549828', '4add1867-32f4-4871-aa48-c683114039ce', '4add1867-32f4-4871-aa48-c683114039ce'),
      ('78c94069-f5da-4e73-a266-27704eda9d14', 'd824b0c1-df1b-40fd-8501-a60670bcbaff', 'description', 'Where designated as a Significant Data Fiduciary, appoint a qualified Data Protection Officer responsible for overseeing privacy compliance and regulatory engagement. Establish a structured Data Protection Impact Assessment (DPIA) process to evaluate high-risk personal data processing activities.', '2026-04-07T18:00:22.214777', '2026-04-07T18:00:22.214777', '4add1867-32f4-4871-aa48-c683114039ce', '4add1867-32f4-4871-aa48-c683114039ce'),
