      ('89780377-58c9-4209-b48e-eea74f455741', 'd8e7688b-8ebe-43c7-a652-234d5d05e742', 'description', 'Security alerts generated from monitoring systems are reviewed, triaged, and escalated according to defined operational procedures. Structured triage ensures that genuine threats are rapidly identified while minimizing false positives. Clear escalation paths help ensure timely response and coordination during security events.', '2026-04-06T15:17:20.245299', '2026-04-06T15:17:20.245299', 'af88f921-2e07-48aa-a3e5-c556a2b2c223', 'af88f921-2e07-48aa-a3e5-c556a2b2c223'),
