      ('8be952df-9ef5-45c5-8636-7f06ef651a80', '7c72fd6d-8385-4136-acb6-147f88156d97', 'description', 'Define a formal information classification scheme that categorizes information based on confidentiality, integrity, and availability requirements. The scheme ensures that sensitive or critical information receives appropriate protection proportional to its business value and risk exposure.', '2026-04-08T17:01:44.377349', '2026-04-09T04:25:49.713986', 'af88f921-2e07-48aa-a3e5-c556a2b2c223', 'af88f921-2e07-48aa-a3e5-c556a2b2c223'),
