      ('a958d897-c3d8-4ef4-aea0-ffb938a13160', '29ba58f4-01cc-4ea8-99c2-742f36cc2e2c', 'name', 'Define Personal Data Retention Schedule', '2026-04-07T18:51:52.566198', '2026-04-07T18:51:52.566198', '4add1867-32f4-4871-aa48-c683114039ce', '4add1867-32f4-4871-aa48-c683114039ce'),
      ('a9ae679d-9ccf-4c4b-aecc-fffc8fe2e8a2', '853f012c-e00c-4b6f-9002-edef9dffc7ba', 'guidance', 'Integrate identity systems and authentication logs with centralized security monitoring or SIEM solutions.', '2026-04-06T15:17:17.596064', '2026-04-06T15:17:17.596064', 'af88f921-2e07-48aa-a3e5-c556a2b2c223', 'af88f921-2e07-48aa-a3e5-c556a2b2c223'),
      ('aa16036b-abef-46f5-aa58-fcbfeb9f4f2e', 'b4e9ec66-8d8c-4094-a8d6-fca76cedb459', 'implementation_guidance', '["Appoint a Data Protection Officer or designated privacy lead responsible for DPDP compliance oversight", "Define roles and responsibilities for data protection across legal, IT, security, and business units", "Establish a governance committee or steering group to review data protection risks and compliance status", "Develop and maintain a documented data protection policy aligned with DPDP requirements", "Conduct periodic governance reviews to assess compliance status and policy effectiveness"]', '2026-04-07T18:00:21.677803', '2026-04-07T18:00:21.677803', '4add1867-32f4-4871-aa48-c683114039ce', '4add1867-32f4-4871-aa48-c683114039ce'),
      ('aa180fef-904e-4348-9957-e66ee21558ab', '58f06dce-a956-4fc2-8296-d00129e311cd', 'description', 'Ensure all ISMS-related documented information such as policies, procedures, standards, and records are properly created, approved, version-controlled, stored, and protected from unauthorized modification or loss.', '2026-04-09T04:20:31.993586', '2026-04-09T04:25:49.713986', 'af88f921-2e07-48aa-a3e5-c556a2b2c223', 'af88f921-2e07-48aa-a3e5-c556a2b2c223'),
      ('aa1c13d7-b86a-40bc-9a66-b0b3ffd548cd', '8d92e6ee-7eb0-4ace-92ca-e2b7a0f4c7d9', 'description', 'Define and maintain a documented incident response process specifically addressing personal data breaches. The procedure should cover identification, containment, investigation, remediation, and internal escalation to ensure rapid and coordinated response to incidents affecting digital personal data.', '2026-04-07T18:00:22.013221', '2026-04-07T18:00:22.013221', '4add1867-32f4-4871-aa48-c683114039ce', '4add1867-32f4-4871-aa48-c683114039ce'),
      ('aa1ffe37-680b-4dee-8eba-48d37e6fb5a2', 'e570c128-6597-46ce-929d-51ffa4dbfa12', 'guidance', 'Use layered physical security controls including access badges, visitor management, and surveillance systems.', '2026-04-08T17:01:44.377349', '2026-04-09T04:25:49.713986', 'af88f921-2e07-48aa-a3e5-c556a2b2c223', 'af88f921-2e07-48aa-a3e5-c556a2b2c223'),
      ('aa7b2ed8-7a87-4cf2-957c-66e8a24beea2', 'd2877bb5-08bd-48e3-9d3c-8d70455e7703', 'acceptance_criteria', '["Security logs cannot be modified by unauthorized users", "Log integrity verification mechanisms are implemented", "Unauthorized log access attempts are monitored"]', '2026-04-07T18:36:49.912712', '2026-04-07T18:36:49.912712', '4add1867-32f4-4871-aa48-c683114039ce', '4add1867-32f4-4871-aa48-c683114039ce'),
      ('aad6ec4f-2041-41eb-a07a-67923b70c20d', 'a7ff3eaa-2d5c-4086-a546-ee387abaaa68', 'description', 'Establish and maintain an accurate inventory of all information assets including hardware, software, virtual systems, data repositories, and cloud resources to ensure visibility and accountability for organizational assets.', '2026-04-08T17:01:44.377349', '2026-04-09T04:25:49.713986', 'af88f921-2e07-48aa-a3e5-c556a2b2c223', 'af88f921-2e07-48aa-a3e5-c556a2b2c223'),
      ('ab0a6cab-47f7-4038-b93c-08a7e7bf63cd', '7072c489-e02e-4873-8b7e-962c4487140f', 'description', 'Implement procedures to ensure information assets are classified, labeled, and handled according to their sensitivity and criticality throughout their lifecycle.', '2026-04-08T17:01:44.377349', '2026-04-09T04:25:49.713986', 'af88f921-2e07-48aa-a3e5-c556a2b2c223', 'af88f921-2e07-48aa-a3e5-c556a2b2c223'),
      ('ab45528a-3930-45eb-8a99-a01a16a35292', 'a9a10778-3b51-4d71-b4ee-17a7a6cb9c9b', 'description', 'Regularly test backup restoration and system recovery procedures to ensure they function effectively during real disruptions. Testing validates that systems and data can be recovered within defined recovery objectives.', '2026-04-08T17:01:44.377349', '2026-04-09T04:25:49.713986', 'af88f921-2e07-48aa-a3e5-c556a2b2c223', 'af88f921-2e07-48aa-a3e5-c556a2b2c223'),
      ('ab64f667-7b44-4cda-a936-505b43f60c8c', 'ba09e807-6318-4c6c-9f62-e2c8c1ce0b48', 'description', 'User identities and accounts are centrally managed across systems to ensure that access is granted, modified, and revoked in accordance with approved employment status and business needs. The process enforces consistent identity lifecycle management from onboarding through role changes and termination. This reduces the likelihood of orphaned or unauthorized accounts remaining active.', '2026-04-06T15:17:15.037142', '2026-04-06T15:17:15.037142', 'af88f921-2e07-48aa-a3e5-c556a2b2c223', 'af88f921-2e07-48aa-a3e5-c556a2b2c223'),
      ('aba807d5-fbec-4a79-9653-39ca6b8a4c15', '20b8d630-fda1-4a25-af6c-4487ea86244b', 'guidance', 'Review data collection forms and system schemas to eliminate unnecessary personal data fields.', '2026-04-07T18:44:27.786296', '2026-04-07T18:44:27.786296', '4add1867-32f4-4871-aa48-c683114039ce', '4add1867-32f4-4871-aa48-c683114039ce'),
      ('ac5c0365-b1fa-46f6-8c3e-f97da5dd179f', 'daae86b7-1c1d-4e34-90ad-f7da4eaa49df', 'guidance', 'Configure identity systems and authentication platforms with automated lockout and inactivity management policies.', '2026-04-06T15:17:18.943177', '2026-04-06T15:17:18.943177', 'af88f921-2e07-48aa-a3e5-c556a2b2c223', 'af88f921-2e07-48aa-a3e5-c556a2b2c223'),
      ('acadcab0-a54c-443c-9a8d-08bb0a8f14a1', 'af2d3edb-6ff0-4026-826b-23300f3a1813', 'description', 'Application code, infrastructure-as-code templates, and critical configuration files are managed through version control systems. Version control enables traceability of modifications, maintains a history of changes, and allows secure collaboration among authorized developers. It also supports rapid rollback and forensic analysis if an issue or unauthorized change occurs.', '2026-04-06T15:17:25.455336', '2026-04-06T15:17:25.455336', 'af88f921-2e07-48aa-a3e5-c556a2b2c223', 'af88f921-2e07-48aa-a3e5-c556a2b2c223'),
      ('acfcb52b-04fa-49be-a2d8-de7f7aebc1ef', 'd2877bb5-08bd-48e3-9d3c-8d70455e7703', 'description', 'Protect security logs from modification or deletion by unauthorized users to preserve integrity for investigations and compliance audits.', '2026-04-07T18:36:49.912712', '2026-04-07T18:36:49.912712', '4add1867-32f4-4871-aa48-c683114039ce', '4add1867-32f4-4871-aa48-c683114039ce'),
      ('ad2dd7d0-0e48-4c84-ba1f-bb3589b7c92b', '4fdaa76b-8228-453a-bef7-1ff0aaca8f7c', 'description', 'Access to systems, applications, and data is granted only after documented requests and management approval. The process ensures that users receive only the level of access necessary for their job responsibilities. This reduces the likelihood of unauthorized system access and excessive privilege assignments.', '2026-04-06T15:17:13.114722', '2026-04-06T15:17:13.114722', 'af88f921-2e07-48aa-a3e5-c556a2b2c223', 'af88f921-2e07-48aa-a3e5-c556a2b2c223'),
      ('ada1e889-410e-497b-817a-7b44f8dfe109', '9451f9a2-0949-4625-92cc-27ec042eb5c8', 'description', 'Ensure personal data is used only for the purposes explicitly defined and approved during data collection or lawful processing evaluation. Purpose restriction reduces the risk of unauthorized secondary use or misuse of personal data. Monitoring and access restrictions help enforce adherence to approved purposes.', '2026-04-07T18:00:21.732665', '2026-04-07T18:00:21.732665', '4add1867-32f4-4871-aa48-c683114039ce', '4add1867-32f4-4871-aa48-c683114039ce'),
      ('adfab2a6-62a3-4a38-a29c-74d8af032582', '853f012c-e00c-4b6f-9002-edef9dffc7ba', 'implementation_guidance', '["Collect login, authentication, and authorization events from key systems and identity providers.", "Configure alerts for repeated failed login attempts, impossible travel events, and unusual login times.", "Monitor for unauthorized privilege escalation or access outside approved roles.", "Establish procedures for investigating and responding to access anomaly alerts."]', '2026-04-06T15:17:17.596064', '2026-04-06T15:17:17.596064', 'af88f921-2e07-48aa-a3e5-c556a2b2c223', 'af88f921-2e07-48aa-a3e5-c556a2b2c223'),
      ('ae06475c-5259-482d-8f8c-65b328026b88', '21cadae7-872f-441b-9a54-9ae944b2c5e7', 'name', 'Develop and Approve Information Security Policy', '2026-04-08T17:01:44.377349', '2026-04-09T04:25:49.713986', 'af88f921-2e07-48aa-a3e5-c556a2b2c223', 'af88f921-2e07-48aa-a3e5-c556a2b2c223'),
      ('ae173a0c-391d-4f61-80c6-f976fbc413f6', '5006dd25-c0e4-41d2-8559-550f8faebee8', 'acceptance_criteria', '["Password reset tokens expire within a defined timeframe", "Reset requests and completions are logged", "Administrative account recovery requires additional verification", "Unauthorized reset attempts trigger alerts"]', '2026-04-07T18:29:03.452906', '2026-04-07T18:29:03.452906', '4add1867-32f4-4871-aa48-c683114039ce', '4add1867-32f4-4871-aa48-c683114039ce'),
      ('ae6ecfcd-9f62-455f-b41b-d6fc88f0eff0', '80ca07cf-eb89-4294-aa8e-938b8abb0858', 'implementation_guidance', '["Create and maintain a centralized registry of applications processing personal data", "Record application owner, purpose of processing, and categories of personal data handled", "Update the inventory when new applications are introduced or retired", "Review the inventory periodically to ensure completeness"]', '2026-04-07T19:19:31.394795', '2026-04-07T19:19:31.394795', '4add1867-32f4-4871-aa48-c683114039ce', '4add1867-32f4-4871-aa48-c683114039ce'),
      ('aea65ffb-1430-44a0-821b-0edb62ba3f80', '4e2bb384-902c-4714-866f-9ffb247e3311', 'description', 'Separate conflicting responsibilities to prevent individuals from having end‑to‑end control over critical processes that could lead to misuse, fraud, or unauthorized changes. Segregation of duties reduces the likelihood of insider threats and privilege abuse.', '2026-04-08T17:01:44.377349', '2026-04-09T04:25:49.713986', 'af88f921-2e07-48aa-a3e5-c556a2b2c223', 'af88f921-2e07-48aa-a3e5-c556a2b2c223'),
      ('b0da5e98-1d65-4041-8489-ffac50b9fbe9', 'c7ca56ce-ffe2-4530-b78b-7ee26051aa17', 'description', 'Operational monitoring tools track system performance, availability, and abnormal system behavior that may indicate failures or security incidents. Monitoring includes infrastructure metrics, service availability, resource utilization, and abnormal operational patterns. Early detection of operational anomalies helps prevent service disruptions and enables rapid investigation of potential security issues.', '2026-04-06T15:17:21.54828', '2026-04-06T15:17:21.54828', 'af88f921-2e07-48aa-a3e5-c556a2b2c223', 'af88f921-2e07-48aa-a3e5-c556a2b2c223'),
      ('b0e7d75d-ee43-475b-9cb6-71ab525a7d88', '978bf834-b455-4388-89af-ca0d52980af5', 'name', 'Implement Data Accuracy Validation Procedures', '2026-04-07T18:58:52.662174', '2026-04-07T18:58:52.662174', '4add1867-32f4-4871-aa48-c683114039ce', '4add1867-32f4-4871-aa48-c683114039ce'),
      ('b16c641a-e6e5-4ca6-bc46-e6c3fd9e659b', '7ef84716-a138-494a-849f-8552d5f506b2', 'implementation_guidance', '["Record vendor name, service description, business owner, and data classification involved", "Document systems accessed by the vendor and integration points with internal infrastructure", "Classify vendors by criticality and data sensitivity handled", "Review and update the vendor inventory periodically and when new vendors are introduced"]', '2026-04-06T15:17:29.315175', '2026-04-06T15:17:29.315175', 'af88f921-2e07-48aa-a3e5-c556a2b2c223', 'af88f921-2e07-48aa-a3e5-c556a2b2c223'),
      ('b1c3a1a0-ecbe-4476-8b95-f2086fcff839', '392c6c63-177c-4ff4-af85-c396f8ab033d', 'name', 'Review and Update Information Security Policies Periodically', '2026-04-08T17:01:44.377349', '2026-04-09T04:25:49.713986', 'af88f921-2e07-48aa-a3e5-c556a2b2c223', 'af88f921-2e07-48aa-a3e5-c556a2b2c223'),
      ('b20c682c-7f41-47a0-8519-ab71f2d191f9', '573acf45-ec9f-4635-a188-8c7229490619', 'description', 'Systems collecting personal data must validate that only necessary data fields are collected and processed for the specified purpose.', '2026-04-07T18:29:03.550262', '2026-04-07T18:29:03.550262', '4add1867-32f4-4871-aa48-c683114039ce', '4add1867-32f4-4871-aa48-c683114039ce'),
      ('b20d35a9-7efe-4671-8e8a-e027b8dd741d', 'c8fe0a12-fcc8-42e3-8163-9c55bdcaf363', 'name', 'Maintain Inventory of Information Assets with Assigned Owners', '2026-04-08T17:01:44.377349', '2026-04-09T04:25:49.713986', 'af88f921-2e07-48aa-a3e5-c556a2b2c223', 'af88f921-2e07-48aa-a3e5-c556a2b2c223'),
      ('b3727df2-5ab1-4b9f-bafc-5caba42d22d5', 'e3cc508d-4eb4-43a6-a93a-d8e820ced1a9', 'name', 'Restrict Access to Personal Data Systems', '2026-04-07T19:13:14.44361', '2026-04-07T19:13:14.44361', '4add1867-32f4-4871-aa48-c683114039ce', '4add1867-32f4-4871-aa48-c683114039ce'),
      ('b3b95f02-1689-4a87-a5d8-9e0efe66240e', '81683014-7616-4d66-b72c-cb2d6ad23155', 'implementation_guidance', '["Review forms, APIs, and data intake mechanisms collecting personal data", "Assess necessity of each data element collected", "Remove or restrict unnecessary data fields", "Document justification for collected data attributes"]', '2026-04-07T19:13:14.301928', '2026-04-07T19:13:14.301928', '4add1867-32f4-4871-aa48-c683114039ce', '4add1867-32f4-4871-aa48-c683114039ce'),
      ('b3c687a2-0c42-42d2-932f-cc1a206417eb', 'c9fc9cfd-5fa4-4642-a595-26b42e4941e6', 'guidance', 'Create a governance charter approved by executive management that defines security oversight structures and responsibilities. Review the charter periodically to ensure alignment with organizational changes.', '2026-04-06T15:16:57.207266', '2026-04-06T15:16:57.207266', 'af88f921-2e07-48aa-a3e5-c556a2b2c223', 'af88f921-2e07-48aa-a3e5-c556a2b2c223'),
      ('b3e46508-e1d6-4f5b-8496-438846194f43', '0b09909d-658c-4583-91b5-9c61acd466b1', 'implementation_guidance', '["Define incident severity levels and escalation criteria.", "Establish a security incident response team with clear responsibilities.", "Provide reporting channels for employees and monitoring systems to raise incidents.", "Maintain documented response playbooks for common incident scenarios."]', '2026-04-08T17:01:44.377349', '2026-04-09T04:25:49.713986', 'af88f921-2e07-48aa-a3e5-c556a2b2c223', 'af88f921-2e07-48aa-a3e5-c556a2b2c223'),
      ('b438bc5d-c5d5-4895-b6ee-2e8a2db46819', 'd81a9e2e-4a43-4a3b-b55d-a061d9bfcb36', 'implementation_guidance', '["Create and maintain a record of processing activities (RoPA)", "Document lawful basis for each processing activity", "Require privacy or legal review before introducing new processing activities", "Periodically review processing activities for continued lawful basis"]', '2026-04-07T18:58:48.893819', '2026-04-07T18:58:48.893819', '4add1867-32f4-4871-aa48-c683114039ce', '4add1867-32f4-4871-aa48-c683114039ce'),
      ('b4d9bfa0-a1e4-41b4-98a0-7cacb57528cf', '06c7a2a2-fd07-4722-93ea-08faa4099ad9', 'implementation_guidance', '["Install fire detection and suppression systems in equipment rooms.", "Implement environmental monitoring for temperature, humidity, and power stability.", "Ensure uninterruptible power supplies or backup power systems protect critical infrastructure.", "Position equipment in secure racks or cabinets to prevent tampering or accidental damage."]', '2026-04-08T17:01:44.377349', '2026-04-09T04:25:49.713986', 'af88f921-2e07-48aa-a3e5-c556a2b2c223', 'af88f921-2e07-48aa-a3e5-c556a2b2c223'),
      ('b4de8503-1ea6-4b09-8f99-ebf754c575fd', '04c83c8e-e4e6-4951-acea-6f43493331d7', 'guidance', 'Use a controlled document management platform with versioning and access controls. Regularly review and update documents to ensure accuracy.', '2026-04-06T15:17:00.161767', '2026-04-06T15:17:00.161767', 'af88f921-2e07-48aa-a3e5-c556a2b2c223', 'af88f921-2e07-48aa-a3e5-c556a2b2c223'),
      ('b5197678-23ab-4f38-8c81-be2ed6a5ae39', '9dcafd31-fd62-45ad-8230-5b8241c32421', 'description', 'Deploy technical safeguards to protect digital personal data from unauthorized access, disclosure, alteration, or destruction. Controls should include strong access management, encryption, and secure system configurations proportionate to the sensitivity and volume of personal data processed. This ensures baseline protection across systems storing or processing personal data.', '2026-04-07T18:00:21.970387', '2026-04-07T18:00:21.970387', '4add1867-32f4-4871-aa48-c683114039ce', '4add1867-32f4-4871-aa48-c683114039ce'),
      ('b54ca8a0-81fc-4f34-b523-c1eee0bb6302', 'ab84b5b8-9099-4b0f-8735-db138b4edebc', 'name', 'Perform Vulnerability Scanning and Remediation', '2026-04-08T17:01:44.377349', '2026-04-09T04:25:49.713986', 'af88f921-2e07-48aa-a3e5-c556a2b2c223', 'af88f921-2e07-48aa-a3e5-c556a2b2c223'),
      ('b5711d79-a7fe-4830-a403-79653c390e58', '8c10560c-13fc-40b8-ad63-85028278507c', 'description', 'Exceptions to defined operational or security control activities are formally documented, assessed, and remediated. Tracking deviations ensures that temporary workarounds, failed controls, or process bypasses do not persist unnoticed. This supports continuous improvement and accountability in operational control processes.', '2026-04-06T15:17:14.353424', '2026-04-06T15:17:14.353424', 'af88f921-2e07-48aa-a3e5-c556a2b2c223', 'af88f921-2e07-48aa-a3e5-c556a2b2c223'),
      ('b5f59db3-337f-4dc5-84d9-f6f243171be8', '903688bb-be06-453c-8f4f-5ed38d09361e', 'description', 'Provide regular security awareness training to employees and contractors to ensure they understand security responsibilities, acceptable use rules, and reporting procedures. Training reduces the likelihood of accidental data exposure and strengthens organizational security culture. Participation must be tracked and periodically refreshed.', '2026-04-09T04:13:35.339189', '2026-04-09T04:25:49.713986', 'af88f921-2e07-48aa-a3e5-c556a2b2c223', 'af88f921-2e07-48aa-a3e5-c556a2b2c223'),
      ('b5f7dba9-2cf3-4d13-9d9d-e64ac95e39c2', 'acc1fd26-f64d-4f8f-a185-ec00e9a3810d', 'guidance', 'Notices should be written in clear language and made accessible at the point of data collection.', '2026-04-07T18:58:50.76989', '2026-04-07T18:58:50.76989', '4add1867-32f4-4871-aa48-c683114039ce', '4add1867-32f4-4871-aa48-c683114039ce'),
      ('b63e114c-75c7-4051-96c2-3f7832f363c9', 'e992f232-9689-46fa-8e08-d084493c287f', 'guidance', 'Document role-based security responsibilities in job descriptions or responsibility matrices. Review assignments periodically to ensure coverage of all security functions.', '2026-04-06T15:16:58.161206', '2026-04-06T15:16:58.161206', 'af88f921-2e07-48aa-a3e5-c556a2b2c223', 'af88f921-2e07-48aa-a3e5-c556a2b2c223'),
      ('b6460385-bf4f-47aa-96da-4a4acf3eddec', '0266e7d1-a610-4e26-814e-6df8d4774521', 'description', 'Maintain centralized documentation demonstrating compliance with DPDP obligations.', '2026-04-07T19:36:48.148247', '2026-04-07T19:36:48.148247', '4add1867-32f4-4871-aa48-c683114039ce', '4add1867-32f4-4871-aa48-c683114039ce'),
      ('b6780a29-bf88-4450-9bef-b3749944022a', 'c1014a97-65e3-4708-a81f-5c6f44b101ea', 'acceptance_criteria', '["Security risk assessments are completed before onboarding vendors with system or data access", "Critical vendors provide independent assurance reports or equivalent security evidence", "Vendor risk findings are documented and tracked to remediation", "Vendor reassessments are conducted periodically based on vendor risk tier"]', '2026-04-06T15:44:43.484375', '2026-04-06T15:44:43.484375', 'af88f921-2e07-48aa-a3e5-c556a2b2c223', 'af88f921-2e07-48aa-a3e5-c556a2b2c223'),
      ('b6a74aa7-a56f-4b81-8d3f-524b73b4dc96', '8ee5d368-91b2-4618-ab70-44a0d4b176bd', 'description', 'The organization conducts formal risk assessments at defined intervals to identify threats, vulnerabilities, and potential impacts to information systems and business processes. Assessments evaluate the likelihood and potential impact of risks to determine appropriate mitigation actions. Results inform security strategy, resource allocation, and control implementation priorities.', '2026-04-06T15:17:04.435335', '2026-04-06T15:17:04.435335', 'af88f921-2e07-48aa-a3e5-c556a2b2c223', 'af88f921-2e07-48aa-a3e5-c556a2b2c223'),
      ('b72da179-0645-4a04-9e0f-bee6ec30d76c', 'e6ebcc93-8bb8-403f-a7e4-1c21268a80a9', 'description', 'All deployments and configuration changes performed in production environments are logged and monitored. Logging provides traceability for who performed the change, when it occurred, and what systems were affected. Continuous monitoring of deployment activity helps detect unauthorized or suspicious changes that could compromise system integrity.', '2026-04-06T15:17:26.096089', '2026-04-06T15:17:26.096089', 'af88f921-2e07-48aa-a3e5-c556a2b2c223', 'af88f921-2e07-48aa-a3e5-c556a2b2c223'),
      ('b734c11c-11ea-448e-895b-af4761e8acee', '6face2da-ade4-431a-91e6-174b8d043f60', 'name', 'Implement Personal Data Accuracy Validation Checks', '2026-04-07T19:13:14.244429', '2026-04-07T19:13:14.244429', '4add1867-32f4-4871-aa48-c683114039ce', '4add1867-32f4-4871-aa48-c683114039ce'),
      ('b75261a2-80f8-4837-a216-7263f3358886', 'f141e977-07d6-474b-8e8b-20e7942f4a05', 'implementation_guidance', '["Display privacy notices prominently in websites, applications, and data collection forms", "Include processing purposes, rights of Data Principals, and grievance contact details", "Maintain version-controlled privacy notices to track updates and changes", "Review and update notices whenever new data processing activities are introduced"]', '2026-04-07T18:00:21.803774', '2026-04-07T18:00:21.803774', '4add1867-32f4-4871-aa48-c683114039ce', '4add1867-32f4-4871-aa48-c683114039ce'),
      ('b77299eb-07ff-4e37-b220-6cab039687b6', '4c3b6503-ee7f-47a8-94ec-1ce0e4d18d03', 'implementation_guidance', '["Require badge or biometric authentication for entry into offices, server rooms, and restricted areas.", "Maintain and regularly review access lists for physical entry systems.", "Implement visitor registration procedures including temporary badges and escort requirements.", "Log and retain physical entry records for security monitoring and investigations.", "Immediately revoke building access when personnel leave the organization."]', '2026-04-06T15:17:18.239609', '2026-04-06T15:17:18.239609', 'af88f921-2e07-48aa-a3e5-c556a2b2c223', 'af88f921-2e07-48aa-a3e5-c556a2b2c223'),
      ('b7801513-0ae7-4c28-ad67-5d1f04bc20b1', '736fd12f-02d8-4476-ad1f-f2a546cf44f6', 'implementation_guidance', '["Provision vendor accounts using least privilege and time-bound access where possible", "Segregate vendor access from internal administrative accounts", "Log and monitor vendor activities within systems and infrastructure", "Review vendor access rights periodically and revoke unused or unnecessary access"]', '2026-04-06T15:17:30.493929', '2026-04-06T15:17:30.493929', 'af88f921-2e07-48aa-a3e5-c556a2b2c223', 'af88f921-2e07-48aa-a3e5-c556a2b2c223'),
      ('b7a56d1a-a336-4959-a80b-fb9b9228e85a', '4703eb9d-b0c7-4ce8-aca2-0de8e038a061', 'acceptance_criteria', '["Data collection fields align with defined purposes", "New fields require documented justification"]', '2026-04-07T18:51:51.549195', '2026-04-07T18:51:51.549195', '4add1867-32f4-4871-aa48-c683114039ce', '4add1867-32f4-4871-aa48-c683114039ce'),
