      ('c047b58f-8ca9-4017-bdac-587e1601852a', 'b28bcff1-5d54-40fe-a11a-b34ad6de1e4c', 'description', 'Senior management periodically reviews the effectiveness of the organization''s security control environment, including policies, control performance, and risk posture. These reviews ensure that governance expectations are met and that deficiencies are identified and addressed. Management oversight reinforces accountability and continuous improvement of internal controls.', '2026-04-06T15:16:59.303193', '2026-04-06T15:16:59.303193', 'af88f921-2e07-48aa-a3e5-c556a2b2c223', 'af88f921-2e07-48aa-a3e5-c556a2b2c223'),
