      ('e25ebcb3-edd2-47d0-8bed-97ac29343a87', 'ab045248-5b25-4404-9cfe-e640e6e27508', 'description', 'Organizations must identify and document the lawful basis for each personal data processing activity under the DPDP Act, including consent or legally permitted uses.', '2026-04-07T18:44:23.712969', '2026-04-07T18:44:23.712969', '4add1867-32f4-4871-aa48-c683114039ce', '4add1867-32f4-4871-aa48-c683114039ce'),
